##Deletion of Azure VM (Copy in Single Line)

Select the Subscription: Get-AzContext-->Change the subscription to req one: \
Select-AzSubscription -SubscriptionName CORPPROD--> Give the VM name and command: \
Remove-AzVM -Name azwodaisp00001-->Enter resource group Name: ResourceGroupName: corp-prod-oda-aae

##Azure Subcription Login 

 Select-AzSubscription -SubscriptionName CORPPROD
 
##Azure Resource Deletion 
 
 Select-AzSubscription -SubscriptionName CORPUAT-->Remove-AzResourceGroup -Name "corp-uat-oda-aae"-->Y
 
